			<h1>20 Innovative IT Ideas To Steal</h1> 
			<br clear="all" class="IG_headline_br">
			<span class="IG_byline"><a class="IG_byline" href="/authors/1118">Stacey Peterson</a></span>
			<span class="IG_date"> 09/14/2011</span>
			<span class="IG_dek"><em>InformationWeek 500</em> innovators have creative solutions to not-so-unusual business problems. How can these help your company?</span>
		</div><!-- END: IG_hed_text -->
		
